Package: biomer
Title: User-Friendly Species-to-Biome Classification
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Hans Christian", "Groß", email = "grossc@uni-marburg.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools to visualize biome raster layers and analyze species
    occurrence data in relation to these biomes. The package enables downloading 
    GBIF occurrence records, cleaning coordinate data, and quantifying species 
    occurrences across user-defined biome layers. Additional functions support 
    raster visualization, data loading, and summary generation.
Encoding: UTF-8
